sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Consumer
    participant P as PullMessageProcessor〔R5.5〕
    participant D as DefaultMessageStore〔R5.5〕
    participant Q as ConsumeQueueInterface〔R5.5〕
    participant L as CommitLog〔R5.5〕
    participant T as ManyMessageTransfer〔R5.5〕

    C->>P: topic, queueId, queueOffset
    P->>D: getMessage
    D->>Q: iterateFrom(queueOffset)
    Q-->>D: CqUnit(phyOffset,size,tagsCode)
    D->>D: ConsumeQueue 级过滤
    D->>L: getMessage(phyOffset,size)
    L-->>D: MappedByteBuffer slice
    D->>D: CommitLog 级过滤并组装结果
    D-->>P: GetMessageResult
    P->>T: Header + message buffers
    T-->>C: 写入网络通道
